e.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E通常,|As much as I like?\nIs that really okay?$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$E笑,|Yes. It seems like you eat a lot.$k$pIf that's the case, then you can have\na 'fight' with the castle foodstuffs.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$WaHuh?$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$Eキメ,|You may have given up before,\nbut that'll be real non-standard training.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes...Lord Marx.\nI'll...do my best.$k
